    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large heavy knives with a single-edged blade, used for cutting cane and clearing plant growth; also used as cutting weapons.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
